\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Independent Institute of Education \'28IIE\'29 is a private higher education Institution registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and also has programmes accredited by the CHE. \line \line The Institution is currently applying for the accreditation of the Higher Certificate in Hospitality Management programme which will be offered in a contact mode of delivery at Johannesburg\'2C IIE PHS\'2C Rosebank and as well as Stellenbosch\'2C IIE PHS\'2C Stellenbosch campus. \line \line The Institution has also applied for the accreditation of a Bachelor of Hospitality Management  . \line \line IIE is accredited to offer a Bachelor of Business Administration in Hospitality Management\'2C as well as a Diploma in Travel and Tourism Management.\cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
